4.  Executive summary

The current document details the list of HELOISA tasks, milestones and deliverables and their respective provisional start and end times, along with delivery dates and relevant SOW requirements. In chapter two we provide the control panel which is used to track all the aforementioned components and the respective responsibles. In chapter three we provide a respective Gantt Chart with the timelines.

2.           Project control panel

A detailed sheet (Axis3_Water_Control_Panel.xlsx) is used to track in one page:

●       Deliverables

●       Milestones

●       Work packages

●       Sub tasks

●       Owner

●       Occurrence

●       SOW

Sheet provides a detailed overview, with color coding to effectively track dependencies and delivery dates.

 

 

3.           Gantt chart

A detailed Gannt chart (A3W_Schedule_2025_01.mpp) has been developed and used, to track actual work at day level.
